      "title": "👑 Pixaroma - Note - START HERE",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# MODELS AND NODES USED IN THIS WORKFLOW  \n\n---\n\n### Put all models in the models folder, organized into their respective subfolders. \n### If a required folder doesn’t exist, create it.\n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Load Diffusion Model\n### Download **Wan2_1-I2V-14B-480p_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled_KJ.safetensors**  from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy_fp8_scaled/resolve/main/I2V/Wan2_1-I2V-14B-480p_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled_KJ.safetensors)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/wan2.1` \n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Load LoRA\n### Download **lightx2v_I2V_14B_480p_cfg_step_distill_rank64_bf16.safetensors**  from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy/resolve/main/Lightx2v/lightx2v_I2V_14B_480p_cfg_step_distill_rank64_bf16.safetensors)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/loras/wan2.2` \n\n---\n\n## 🟣 ModelPatchLoader\n### Download **wan2.1_infiniteTalk_single_fp16.safetensors** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Wan_2.1_ComfyUI_repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/model_patches/wan2.1_infiniteTalk_single_fp16.safetensors)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/model_patches` \n\n---\n\n## 🟣 AudioEncoderLoader\n### Download **wav2vec2-chinese-base_fp16.safetensors** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/wav2vec2_safetensors/resolve/main/wav2vec2-chinese-base_fp16.safetensors)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/audio_encoders` \n\n---\n\n## 🟣 Load CLIP\n\n###  Download **umt5_xxl_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled.safetensors** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Wan_2.1_ComfyUI_repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/umt5_xxl_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled.safetensors)\n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders`  \n\n--- \n\n## 🟣 Load VAE\n\n### Download the **Wan2_1_VAE_bf16.safetensors** from [HERE](https://huggingface.co/Kijai/WanVideo_comfy/resolve/main/Wan2_1_VAE_bf16.safetensors)  \n\n📁 **Place in:** `ComfyUI/models/vae`  \n\n---\n\n## 🧩 Nodes Installed from Manager  \n\n- ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite\n\n---\n\n## 📚 Resources  \n🎥 **Tutorials:** [Pixaroma YouTube Channel](https://www.youtube.com/@pixaroma)  \n💬 **Community Discord:** [Join Here](https://discord.com/invite/gggpkVgBf3)\n"
